Class MetaschemaDataTypeProvider

java.lang.Object
gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.AbstractDataTypeProvider
gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.adapter.MetaschemaDataTypeProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataTypeProvider
public final class MetaschemaDataTypeProvider extends AbstractDataTypeProvider
Provides runtime discovery of built-in implementations of the core Metaschema data types.
